A [Christmas dinner](/Christmas_dinner) plate in Scotland, featuring roast [turkey](/Turkey_(bird)), [roast potatoes](/Potatoes), mashed potatoes and brussels sprouts. A festive spread, designed to be consumed with gusto and followed by a profound nap. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

