[Titanic Belfast](/Titanic_Belfast) museum on the former shipyard in Belfast where the RMS Titanic was built. A monument to ambition, tragedy, and the enduring human fascination with colossal failures. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

