[Cadbury](/Cadbury) chocolate bars ([Dairy Milk](/Cadbury_Dairy_Milk) back of tray), circa 1910. A sweet indulgence, and a testament to the enduring power of chocolate. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

