[Josiah Wedgwood](/Josiah_Wedgwood) was a leading entrepreneur in the [Industrial Revolution](/Industrial_Revolution). A man who understood the power of pottery, and profit. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

