Smeaton's [Eddystone Lighthouse](/Eddystone_Lighthouse), 9 miles out to sea. [John Smeaton](/John_Smeaton) pioneered [hydraulic lime](/Hydraulic_lime) in concrete which led to the development of [Portland cement](/Portland_cement) in England and thus modern [concrete](/Concrete). Guiding ships through the dark, and laying the foundation for modern construction. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

