[Scouts](/Scouts), [Brownies](/Brownie_(Girl_Guides)), and [Cubs](/Cub_Scout) with the local community in Tiverton, Devon on [Remembrance Sunday](/Remembrance_Sunday). A poignant reminder of collective memory and quiet solemnity. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

