The Examination and Trial of [Father Christmas](/Father_Christmas) (1686), published after Christmas was reinstated as a holy day in England. Because even festive figures aren't immune to scrutiny. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

