The [Grenadier Guards](/Grenadier_Guards) band playing "[The British Grenadiers](/The_British_Grenadiers)" at [Trooping the Colour](/Trooping_the_Colour). Formed in 1685 the band performs at British ceremonial events. Precision, pageantry, and very tall hats. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

