One of the UK's many [stately homes](/Stately_homes), [Chatsworth House](/Chatsworth_House) in Derbyshire, surrounded by an [English garden](/English_garden). The house is one of the settings of Jane Austen's novel [Pride and Prejudice](/Pride_and_Prejudice_(novel)). Grandeur, history, and probably a rather drafty interior. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

