Animator [Nick Park](/Nick_Park) with his [Wallace and Gromit](/Wallace_and_Gromit) characters. A plasticine duo, capturing the eccentricities of British invention and companionship. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

