[R. White's](/R._White%27s_Lemonade) [soft drinks](/Soft_drink) sold in London. Selling carbonated [lemonade](/Lemonade) in 1845, by 1887 they sold strawberry soda, raspberry soda and cherryade. Refreshment, then as now, a welcome distraction. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

