A [Watt steam engine](/Watt_steam_engine), the [steam engine](/Steam_engine) that propelled the [Industrial Revolution](/Industrial_Revolution) in Britain and the world. The very engine of progress, for better or worse. (from [Culture of the United Kingdom](/Culture_of_the_United_Kingdom) )

